/// Generic enum with bare (Unit) variants — α parse-signal.
/// Isolates the type-param-on-enum head: `Maybe<T>` with no named-field payload.
/// RED (pre step-2): `<T>` after the enum name produces ERROR nodes.
/// GREEN (step-2): `optional($.type_parameters)` added to enum_declaration.
